metadata.name: KAMI #1
metadata.description: A collection of 10,000 transcendent NFTs minted on the Ethereum blockchain. Each KAMI is randomly generated from a combination of over 150 hand-drawn traits. Your KAMI doubles as your key to the Kamiverse. Devine or Demonic? They have walked amongst us throughout history, hidden in plain sight. As their story unfolds, the legend of the KAMI is reborn.
